WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.180
In this dream, the Lord showed me

00:00:04.019 --> 00:00:08.760
a massive earthquake that was

00:00:06.180 --> 00:00:12.780
going to happen in America. It was the New

00:00:08.760 --> 00:00:15.780
Madrid fault, and this was

00:00:12.780 --> 00:00:18.060
literally the largest

00:00:15.780 --> 00:00:21.119
earthquake that had ever happened on the

00:00:18.060 --> 00:00:25.380
Earth. Whenever I saw it in my

00:00:21.119 --> 00:00:28.019
dream, it happened right by the

00:00:25.380 --> 00:00:30.180
Mississippi River, and

00:00:28.019 --> 00:00:33.000
it split the Mississippi River and

00:00:30.180 --> 00:00:35.700
made it bigger.

00:00:33.000 --> 00:00:38.160
All the bridges that were on the

00:00:35.700 --> 00:00:40.320
Mississippi River collapsed, and they

00:00:38.160 --> 00:00:43.319
were all down. The Lord showed

00:00:40.320 --> 00:00:46.379
me things were on fire; it was

00:00:43.320 --> 00:00:48.840
total devastation.

00:00:46.379 --> 00:00:51.239
I could see it went clear down to the

00:00:48.840 --> 00:00:53.940
New Orleans area and clear

00:00:51.239 --> 00:00:56.940
up into the Chicago area. It was

00:00:53.940 --> 00:01:00.120
massive. As I said,

00:00:56.940 --> 00:01:03.239
all the bridges fell, so

00:01:00.120 --> 00:01:05.700
there was no way for semi-trucks to

00:01:03.239 --> 00:01:09.539
go from east to west.

00:01:05.700 --> 00:01:11.700
They brought in these bridges from

00:01:09.540 --> 00:01:13.680
the Army; they were like floating

00:01:11.700 --> 00:01:16.320
bridges. The Army brought them in and

00:01:13.680 --> 00:01:18.659
put them in all up and down

00:01:16.320 --> 00:01:20.699
where the highways were, trying to make

00:01:18.659 --> 00:01:23.159
it so trucks could come in and out

00:01:20.700 --> 00:01:25.320
for emergencies. But they couldn't get

00:01:23.159 --> 00:01:27.299
the trucks from east to west, so they

00:01:25.320 --> 00:01:29.699
brought in planes.

00:01:27.299 --> 00:01:34.140
They flew the

00:01:29.700 --> 00:01:35.579
food into cities where the semi-trucks

00:01:34.140 --> 00:01:37.140
couldn't get back and forth,

00:01:35.579 --> 00:01:39.539
bringing the food in

00:01:37.140 --> 00:01:41.880
humongous cargo

00:01:39.540 --> 00:01:43.920
planes so

00:01:41.880 --> 00:01:46.380
that the food could get throughout

00:01:43.920 --> 00:01:48.479
all the cities in America. In

00:01:46.380 --> 00:01:52.259
another dream, the Lord showed

00:01:48.479 --> 00:01:54.840
me massive helicopters,

00:01:52.259 --> 00:01:57.600
Chinook helicopters, and they were flying

00:01:54.840 --> 00:02:00.420
from the west. I stood on the

00:01:57.600 --> 00:02:04.679
back porch in my dream and I could

00:02:00.420 --> 00:02:08.280
visibly smell fire in

00:02:04.680 --> 00:02:09.720
the air. It was so strong; it

00:02:08.280 --> 00:02:11.280
was like the haze

00:02:09.720 --> 00:02:13.680
you see from a fire

00:02:11.280 --> 00:02:15.660
whenever there is a grass fire. I

00:02:13.680 --> 00:02:19.080
could hear the helicopters

00:02:15.660 --> 00:02:22.440
flying low, and they were all coming

00:02:19.080 --> 00:02:24.239
in lines, in formation.

00:02:22.440 --> 00:02:26.040
The helicopters

00:02:24.239 --> 00:02:27.599
were coming from the West Coast and

00:02:26.040 --> 00:02:30.120
going to the East Coast.

00:02:27.599 --> 00:02:32.579
Where I live is in the

00:02:30.120 --> 00:02:34.800
central part of America, so you could

00:02:32.580 --> 00:02:37.800
hear them coming.

00:02:34.800 --> 00:02:40.620
They were so loud because there were so

00:02:37.800 --> 00:02:43.080
many of them at a time, all flying

00:02:40.620 --> 00:02:44.760
in formation. There were

00:02:43.080 --> 00:02:46.860
probably 30 or 40 of them at a time, and

00:02:44.760 --> 00:02:51.060
it would

00:02:46.860 --> 00:02:53.940
shake the houses.

00:02:51.060 --> 00:02:57.060
I didn't watch

00:02:53.940 --> 00:02:59.640
TV in the dream, but I knew that

00:02:57.060 --> 00:03:01.440
it was just like a 9/11 event; it was that

00:02:59.640 --> 00:03:04.738
big, something that shook

00:03:01.440 --> 00:03:06.840
America. Everything

00:03:04.739 --> 00:03:09.060
was quiet. I could look across

00:03:06.840 --> 00:03:11.280
at my neighbors, but nobody was outside;

00:03:09.060 --> 00:03:15.180
they were all inside watching

00:03:11.280 --> 00:03:18.420
what happened on TV. Then

00:03:15.180 --> 00:03:22.680
the Lord took my eyes

00:03:18.420 --> 00:03:26.040
in the dream to a stone lion's face. I

00:03:22.680 --> 00:03:28.680
was asking,

00:03:26.040 --> 00:03:31.260
'What is that?'because I saw

00:03:28.680 --> 00:03:35.280
the stone

00:03:31.260 --> 00:03:38.760
lion face. All of a sudden in the

00:03:35.280 --> 00:03:40.860
dream, He said, 'Look at the Stock

00:03:38.760 --> 00:03:43.620
Exchange, the New York Stock Exchange.'I

00:03:40.860 --> 00:03:47.280
didn't know where this lion

00:03:43.620 --> 00:03:50.459
face was, so I woke up the next day and

00:03:47.280 --> 00:03:51.239
looked up

00:03:51.239 --> 00:03:55.680
the Stock

00:03:53.280 --> 00:03:58.260
Exchange. On the top of the building, there are

00:03:55.680 --> 00:04:01.560
lions all along the top, and it was

00:03:58.260 --> 00:04:04.440
the exact lion. In the

00:04:01.560 --> 00:04:07.080
dream, I could see the streets of New

00:04:04.440 --> 00:04:08.879
York, and they were completely desolate. I

00:04:07.080 --> 00:04:11.459
could see tumbleweeds, which was weird

00:04:08.879 --> 00:04:14.220
because I know there are no tumbleweeds in

00:04:11.459 --> 00:04:16.620
New York, but I saw them going

00:04:14.220 --> 00:04:19.199
down the street. It was desolate;

00:04:16.620 --> 00:04:22.199
there was nobody moving around. It was

00:04:19.199 --> 00:04:24.780
completely blank, like the

00:04:22.199 --> 00:04:27.300
people had all gone and were hiding out,

00:04:24.780 --> 00:04:28.799
because the whole

00:04:27.300 --> 00:04:30.900
government and everything was shut down

00:04:28.800 --> 00:04:33.060
again, kind of like COVID was. It was

00:04:30.900 --> 00:04:35.219
really weird.

00:04:35.220 --> 00:04:40.680
For a

00:04:38.340 --> 00:04:42.919
long time, those helicopters

00:04:40.680 --> 00:04:46.259
were going towards the Mississippi area.

00:04:42.919 --> 00:04:48.479
Then the Lord showed me another

00:04:46.259 --> 00:04:51.660
earthquake; it was like

00:04:48.479 --> 00:04:54.960
an aftershock that happened by the Texarkana

00:04:51.660 --> 00:04:57.600
area and went clear up to Tulsa,

00:04:54.960 --> 00:04:59.159
Oklahoma. I could see that it was

00:04:57.600 --> 00:05:02.100
probably a magnitude 6

00:04:59.160 --> 00:05:04.620
or bigger. But the one that

00:05:02.100 --> 00:05:09.180
hit the Mississippi Valley area was like

00:05:04.620 --> 00:05:12.240
a 10.0. I could see

00:05:09.180 --> 00:05:14.460
that all the houses built on

00:05:12.240 --> 00:05:17.220
cinder blocks—houses

00:05:14.460 --> 00:05:20.219
not on a flat slab—were

00:05:17.220 --> 00:05:23.639
completely destroyed. In this,

00:05:20.220 --> 00:05:24.960
1,800 people died. The Lord

00:05:23.639 --> 00:05:28.020
was showing me the people who had

00:05:24.960 --> 00:05:30.120
perished in the dream where all of the

00:05:28.020 --> 00:05:32.940
houses were completely leveled and

00:05:30.120 --> 00:05:35.220
flattened from this massive earthquake.

00:05:35.220 --> 00:05:40.380
I don't know why it happens or

00:05:37.380 --> 00:05:42.780
when it happens; all I know is that I

00:05:40.380 --> 00:05:45.539
saw this and have prayed over it.

00:05:42.780 --> 00:05:47.880
I feel that it's about to happen soon.

00:05:45.539 --> 00:05:49.800
Like I said, it could happen in the

00:05:47.880 --> 00:05:51.360
fall, it could happen in the spring,

00:05:49.800 --> 00:05:53.759
or it could be years from now.

00:05:51.360 --> 00:05:55.560
I just see these things; the Lord

00:05:53.759 --> 00:05:58.440
gives them to me, and I pray over them. It was

00:05:55.560 --> 00:06:02.100
just something

00:05:58.440 --> 00:06:04.979
heavy on my heart to share. If

00:06:02.100 --> 00:06:06.660
you have seen this or

00:06:04.979 --> 00:06:08.400
heard of anyone who has, you

00:06:06.660 --> 00:06:11.639
can comment in the comment

00:06:08.400 --> 00:06:13.020
section. I appreciate

00:06:11.639 --> 00:06:14.759
you following me.

00:06:13.020 --> 00:06:16.258
I have more things that I

00:06:14.759 --> 00:06:19.259
want to share, but I want to do it

00:06:16.259 --> 00:06:21.120
on separate videos for what I feel

00:06:19.259 --> 00:06:22.919
the Lord has shown me is coming.

00:06:21.120 --> 00:06:26.600
I really appreciate it.

00:06:22.919 --> 00:06:26.599
Thank you all very much. Bye-bye.

